== Overview ==
The Syphon Immobiliser is a heavy duty [[:Category:Weapons (Power Disruptors)|draining weapon]]. Its awesome power is designed to sap the energy from enemy bots, tanks and warships.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Syphon Immobiliser can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
